**************replace***************
str1="abc"
print(str1.replace('a','o')       ========>>>>>>>>obc


to replace lot of letters in given string then use maketrans static function

example:if we want replace a with z
                           b with y
                           c with x
                           like this ......
                           
1.step :map
a="abc"
b="zyx"
mapped=str.maketrans(a,b)

string1="abokc"
res=string1.translate(mapped)
print(res)  =============>>>>>>>>>>> zyokx







